    "lede": "These clusters answer most of what businesses ask about bookkeeping engagements. The remainder are specific to your situation &mdash; the current state of your books, your industry, transaction volume, the exact problem you&rsquo;re looking at. Book a 30-minute discovery call to get answers from a Certified ProAdvisor on your specific circumstances. Complimentary, no obligation, no hourly billing.",
